      "content": "hey, i am working on a new horror anthology and i need some ideas for settings. i want something that feels gritty and a bit unsettling, like a part of a big city that people are actually afraid to walk through at night. can you help me brainstorm some urban locations that have that creepy, dangerous vibe?",
